text:
Photo flash! - live from the trials of '' adrian '' (broadcast tomorrow night), the bomb-guests

06 Nov 2019, 17:06


PHOTO FLASH! - DIRECTLY FROM THE TESTS OF '' ADRIAN '' (IN TOMORROW TOMORROW), THE HEAVY ARTILLERY WHICH HAS DEFINED CELENTANO: CHIAMBRETTI, GILETTI, SCOTTI, CONTI AND BONOLIS. THE EVENING OF CANALE5, AFTER THE LESSONS OF THE LAST YEAR, EXPECTS ITSELF AS A TV EVENT OF THOSE WHO CAPTIVE ONCE EVERY 20 YEARS ...
